## Phase 1 — You Run the Program

```
You type: java MusicPlayer
               ↓
OS receives the command
               ↓
OS creates a NEW PROCESS (JVM)
               ↓
Assigns a PID (example: PID 10245)
               ↓
Allocates memory for JVM process
```

