## Phase 7 — playSong() Executes

```
⏰ Time: 0s
main thread calls player.playSong()
          ↓
New Stack Frame pushed for playSong()

┌──────────────────────────────┐
│  MAIN THREAD STACK           │
│  ┌────────────────────────┐  │
│  │  playSong() frame ←TOP │  │  ← CPU working here
│  ├────────────────────────┤  │
│  │  main() frame          │  │  ← waiting
│  └────────────────────────┘  │
└──────────────────────────────┘

CPU executes line by line:
→ prints "▶ Playing song started..."
→ hits Thread.sleep(5000)
→ main thread PAUSES for 5 seconds
→ CPU is BLOCKED — doing nothing useful! 😴
→ after 5s prints "✅ Song played!"
→ playSong() frame POPPED from stack

⏰ Time: 5s — playSong() done!
```

