## ❌ The Big Problem

```
Without Multithreading:

playSong()     → 5s  → CPU blocked 😴
downloadSong() → 8s  → CPU blocked 😴
likeSong()     → 2s  → CPU blocked 😴

→ Methods execute ONE BY ONE
→ Next method WAITS for previous to finish
→ User cannot like song while downloading!
→ User cannot play song while downloading!
→ Total waste of CPU time!
→ Poor user experience!
```

