## 📊 Without vs With Multithreading

| | Without Multithreading | With Multithreading |
|---|---|---|
| **Threads** | 1 (main only) | 4 (main + 3) |
| **Execution** | Sequential | Parallel |
| **playSong** | 0s → 5s | 0s → 5s |
| **downloadSong** | 5s → 13s | 0s → 8s |
| **likeSong** | 13s → 15s | 0s → 2s |
| **Total Time** | 15 seconds 🐢 | 8 seconds 🚀 |
| **CPU Usage** | Blocked mostly | Efficient |
| **User Experience** | Poor ❌ | Good ✅ |

